rComments: The prof is very engaging and passionate about the subject. She uses real life examples to help you understand the course material and actually see value in what youre learning and how you will be able to apply this knowledge in the real world. I hated tech in first year so this course was definitely an upgrade. Cheers Lysanne

Terrible class, pure memorization. Slides with paragraphs of information and still makes you read the book even though the slides are copy-paste of the textbook. Reminds of a high school teacher and class. Sit, listen and try not to fall asleep. The only good thing about COVID was that I didn't have to go to her class anymore

There are online quizzes every week only 5 were graded, she sometimes adds questions about stuff only in the book and not on the slides so read the books but other than that the quizzes are easy and helps with studying, midterm is word for word slides multiple choice and some book questions, final was a bit harder but if you read slides you're good
teacherRatingTags: ['Clear grading criteria', 'Graded by few things', 'Group projects']

rComments: Most boring class ever, pure theory and studying for this class is so painful. You need to memorize a lot and it's things that you will forget 15 mins after the final. She gives quizzes every week which and doesn't tell us if its evaluated or not until the day of. Still a good prof but she should make the midterm and final a little easier...

Je ne sais pas si c'est le cours comme tel ou bien le prof, mais je n'a vraiment pas aimé la matière. Cours 100% théorique, de la mémorisation pure. Et le prof devrait enseigner en conséquence. Livre obligatoire. Il n'y a aucune grille donnée aux élèves pour les cas!!! Frustrant!! Soyez prêts à lire mes amis...

Cette prof est une bonne oratrice et ses examens sont justes.  Cependant, c'est un cours très théorique, et ses nombreuses diapos ne couvrent pas tout la matière du livre, donc il faut tout lire le manuel aussi. Il y a des quiz hebdomadaires qui sont piégés et des cas aux deux semaines dont les attentes ne sont pas du tout claires...

The teacher itself was good, however she had a boring class to teach to begin with, but gives you good complete powerpoint so you don't really have to go to class anyways if theres no case study that day.

Elle parle tout le temps... Beaucoup trop de slides PowerPoint... Bref, long et ennuyant !  Elle devrait intégrer plus dactivités dans ses classes !  Sincèrement, je trouve qu'elle se donne un air de supériorité, et ça me tanne !
